event.title: Public Money? Public Code! panel in Berlin, Germany

body.p: During the Nextcloud conference in Berlin our policy analyst Alexander Sander will participate at a panel about "Public Money? Public Code!". The panel takes place on Saturday, 14th at 12, at the TU Berlin, Stra√üe des 17. Juni 136, Berlin. Nextcloud kindly provided a voucher for free entrance to the whole FSFE community.
